Onaka ga suita;I'm hungry
Nani o tabemasu ka;What will you eat?
Yūshoku o tsukutte imasu;I'm cooking dinner
Kore wa totemo oishii desu;It's very delicious
Piza ga suki desu;I like pizza
Mō sukura pan o totte;Take some more bread
Sakana wa suki ja arimasen;I don't like fish
Mizu o moraemasu ka;Can I have some water?
Kissaten ni ikimasu;We're going to a cafe
Ocha ga suki desu;I prefer tea
Amasukisugimasu;It's too sweet
Watashi no supūn wa doko desu ka;Where is my spoon?
Daietto chū desu;I'm on a diet
Itadakimasu;Bon appetit
Onaka ga ippai desu;I'm full
Kono ryōri wa karai desu;This dish is spicy
Fōku o kudasai;Give me a fork
Watashi wa bejitarian desu;I'm vegetarian
Kono kēki o tabete mite;Try this cake
Onaka ga suite imasen;I'm not hungry
